After navigating away from my form and back, the autofill dialog appears in the wrong place.  I tested this on an Android emulator, not sure about iOS.

<img width="200" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/389558/178375854-9f59f14b-b729-4256-a5af-5cc967daf86f.png" />

### Steps to reproduce

  1. Run the app below, which has some autofillable fields in a route.
  2. Navigate to the route.
  3. Tap the field.  The autofill dialog shows in the correct place.
  4. Press the back button.
  5. Navigate back to the page with the field.
  6. Tap the field again.

Expected: The autofill dialog appears near the field.
Actual: It appears at the bottom left corner of the screen.

